    • Notification

    • Notification

      public Notification(String notificationId, String userId, String title, String message, boolean isRead, LocalDateTime createdAt)
      Instantiates a new notification with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      notificationId - the unique identifier for the notification
      userId - the identifier of the recipient user
      title - the title of the notification
      message - the message content of the notification
      isRead - the status indicating if the notification has been read
      createdAt - the timestamp when the notification was created
